window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I'll cheat death itself to save the woman I love. Impossible...for anyone but Doctor Undying!</b></p> <p>Freed from parole, I’m free to mentor the beautiful villainesses under my care. But my ultimate goal remains Project Rebirth and saving my lover, Green Phoenix.</p> <p>The key to these experiments appears at a supervillain auction being held in the kingdom of an immortal tyrant. Countless obstacles, upstart wannabes, and an unexpected foe from my past, stand in our way.</p> <p>Send your tanks, your monsters, and your army of misshapen clones against me, I’ll crush them all to claim what is rightfully mine!</p>"; 
